## Our Commitment to AI Transparency

{{ business_name }} is committed to the responsible and transparent use of artificial intelligence (AI) in our operations. This statement explains how we use AI, what safeguards we have in place, and how you can contact us with questions or concerns.

This statement is published in accordance with Australia's **8 AI Ethics Principles**, the **AI6 Guidance for AI Adoption** (October 2024), and the **POLA Act 2024** transparency obligations.

