### Customer-Facing AI

{{ business_name }} uses AI to assist with customer-facing content and services. All AI-generated customer-facing content is {% if ai_generated_content_reviewed %}reviewed by a human before publication{% else %}subject to quality assurance processes{% endif %}.

We do not use AI to impersonate human staff. Where AI-generated content is used in customer communications, we endeavour to disclose this clearly.
