{% endfor %}

In accordance with the **POLA Act 2024** (APP 1.7-1.9, commencing 10 December 2026):
- We disclose the types of personal information used in automated decisions
- We identify whether automated decisions significantly affect individuals
- Individuals may request human review of automated decisions that significantly affect them

