We are committed to **data minimisation** — we only input the minimum data necessary for the AI task and take steps to anonymise or de-identify personal information before AI processing where practicable.

{% if ai_tools_overseas and ai_tools_overseas | length > 0 %}
### Cross-Border Data Processing

Some of our AI tools process data in overseas data centres. In accordance with **APP 8** of the Privacy Act 1988, we take reasonable steps to ensure overseas recipients handle personal information consistently with the APPs. We accept vicarious liability under **Section 16C** for our overseas AI providers' handling of personal information.

